snippet.title: Carnival Games: Monkey See, Monkey Do Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming this April, Exclusively on Kinect for Xbox 360: Carnival Games: Monkey See, Monkey Do.

Carnival Games: Monkey See, Monkey Do is built from the ground up only for Kinect. Twenty totally controller-free new games and attractions allow you to swing into the batting cage, avoid twisting tornadoes in Hot Air Balloon Race, and more. Voice recognition technology even allows The Amazing Wodin, a wily wizard, to advise you of your future. Designed for fun-seekers of all ages and skills, it's is a perfect fit for families everywhere!

ESRB Rating: EVERYONE
